"Simple" Minesweeper game
To play - Run the Main file. 
You will be presented with a grid of mines, may the odds be ever in your favor.
At the top right you will see a timer. This shows how long you have been working on this game.
The smiley face at the top is the reset button. Click inside it to reset the game. 
At the left you will see the difficulty and - + buttons. In order for the new difficulty to work, click the smiley.
Seems simple enough. Good luck :)
